== 開發 ==
本作是繼《[[刺客教條：叛變|刺客教條：叛變]]》後第二部並非由[[育碧蒙特利爾|育碧蒙特利爾]]工作室開發的《[[刺客教條系列|刺客教條系列]]》作品。2014年7月2日，育碧軟件宣佈曾協助開發系列過去六款作品、《刺客教條III：暴君華盛頓》、以及《刺客教條IV：黑旗 自由的吶喊》的[[育碧魁北克|育碧魁北克]]工作室將帶領某重要資產的主要開發工作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-07-03-an-upcoming-assassins-creed-game-will-be-led-by-ubisofts-quebec-studio|title=Upcoming Assassin's Creed game will be the first not headed by Ubisoft Montreal|first=Jeffery|last=Matulef|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2014-07-03|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128124405/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-07-03-an-upcoming-assassins-creed-game-will-be-led-by-ubisofts-quebec-studio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。創意總監由曾參與《[[刺客教條：兄弟會|刺客教條：兄弟會]]》、《[[刺客教條：啟示錄|刺客教條：啟示錄]]》、《[[刺客教條III|刺客教條III]]》與《自由的吶喊》的Marc-Alexis Côté出任<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2014/07/02/ubisoft-expands-its-quebec-city-studio-to-lead-the-future-of-assassins-creed/|title=Ubisoft expands its Quebec City studio to lead the future of Assassin's Creed|first=Jeff|last=Grubb|work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|date=2014-07-02|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921040528/https://venturebeat.com/2014/07/02/ubisoft-expands-its-quebec-city-studio-to-lead-the-future-of-assassins-creed/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/how-assassin-s-creed-syndicate-reinvents-stealth-a/1100-6427220/|title=How Assassin's Creed Syndicate Reinvents Stealth and Combat in the Series|first=Alexa|last=Ray Corriea|date=2015-05-12|accessdate=2015-05-12|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207014857/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/how-assassin-s-creed-syndicate-reinvents-stealth-a/1100-6427220/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，高級監製由François Pelland出任<ref name="7Things" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-05/12/assassins-creed-syndicate-announcement|title=Assassin's Creed: Syndicate industrialises steampunk slayings|first=Matt|last=Kamen|work={{tsl|en|Wired.co.uk|}}|date=2015-05-12|accessdate=2015-05-12|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193214/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-05/12/assassins-creed-syndicate-announcement|dead-url=no}}</ref>，聲效總監由Lydia Andrew出任<ref name="7Things" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/assassin-s-creed-syndicate-story-characters-and-se/1100-6427217/|title=Assassin's Creed Syndicate Story, Characters, and Setting Breakdown|first=Alexa|last=Ray Corriea|date=2015-05-12|accessdate=2015-05-12|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128024301/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/assassin-s-creed-syndicate-story-characters-and-se/1100-6427217/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

遊戲首批資訊於2014年12月2日自網站[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]流出，遊戲當時名為《刺客教條：勝利》（Assassin's Creed Victory），附有遊戲細節和從一段七分鐘遊戲示範片段中截取的圖片。育碧軟件於當天稍後時間確認有關消息，對公司不打算對外公開的內部資產流出市面表示失望，但期待於稍後日子正式公開工作室的已有素材<ref>{{cite web |date=2014-12-02 |title=Next Year's Big Assassin's Creed Is Set In Victorian London [UPDATE] |url=http://kotaku.com/next-years-big-assassins-creed-is-set-in-victorian-lond-1665343788 |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |first=Jason |last=Schreier |accessdate=2015-05-12 |archive-date=2014-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141203051530/http://kotaku.com/next-years-big-assassins-creed-is-set-in-victorian-lond-1665343788 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年5月7日，育碧軟件宣佈公開日被定於5月12日，但包括遊戲正式名稱在內的相關資訊再次於Kotaku提早流出<ref>{{cite web |title=Next Assassin's Creed To Be Announced Next Week; Now Called Syndicate |url=http://kotaku.com/this-years-victorian-assassins-creed-will-be-announced-1702873301 |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |first=Jason |last=Schreier |date=2015-05-07 |accessdate=2015-05-12 |archive-date=2015-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508204840/http://kotaku.com/this-years-victorian-assassins-creed-will-be-announced-1702873301 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；遊戲主角的名字與圖片亦於5月11日被公開<ref>{{cite web|title=Sources: You Can Play As A Woman In Assassin's Creed: Syndicate|url=http://kotaku.com/sources-you-can-play-as-a-woman-in-assassins-creed-sy-1703598017|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|first=Jason|last=Schreier|date=2015-05-11|accessdate=2015-05-11|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140516/http://kotaku.com/sources-you-can-play-as-a-woman-in-assassins-creed-sy-1703598017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

曾為《刺客教條III》擔任顧問的歷史學家Jean-Vincent Roy自2013年5月再次出任顧問<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/assassins-creed-syndicate-female-assassins-and-gang-members-a-step-for-equality|title=Assassin's Creed Syndicate: Female Assassins and Gang Members, A Step for Equality|first=Mike|last=Williams|work=[[USgamer|USgamer]]|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917215703/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/assassins-creed-syndicate-female-assassins-and-gang-members-a-step-for-equality|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年5月12日，育碧在線上公開最新訊息正式定名為梟雄(SYNDICATE)。

